{"tid":1354767,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩同我推爆佢","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:11:44.000Z","uid":276744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f76f0dc63b984392408bf19d8bc8f4a027074ff","tid":1354767,"uid":276744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗事件追究起來，警察管理層可能要坐監</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李漢民、盧偉聰、游乃強<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXdjHhE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXdjHhE.png&h=abe8082d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗這單 case，如果真正追究起來，警察管理層有可能有監坐。<br />\n<br />\n英國上訴庭有個案例，R v Dytham [1979] Q. B. 722，有個差人明明目睹夜總會外有三個人圍毆一個人，但他介入的話，會搞到遲收工，於是當睇唔到，結果被圍的人死了，那差人被刑事控告公職人員行為不當，入罪了，而R v Dytham 那案例，也成為包括香港法庭在內一直被引用的經典案例，終審法院在最近的曾蔭權上訴才提及這案。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來說，身為有責任保護大眾的公職人員而蓄意見死不救，不是黑唔黑的問題了，是坐唔坐的問題。當然，選擇式執法下，一定不會告了。大家都知道，香港的法治很有「特色」，只治反對派，不治權貴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E5%9D%90%E7%9B%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%259D%2590%25E7%259B%25A3%2F&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQUigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=0e438f4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A